<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_460" id="229v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_460_r1l5"><expan>fricʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Eraſem <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l6">Wıſentaw gebrüdern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_460_r1l7"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> f . vnd Eraſem / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie ew vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l10">den ewrn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_460_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr habe </del></ab></add> nu cʒü <expan>Huntſhawbt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_460_r1l8">vnd auf den <expan>güt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jr habe </ab></add> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l11">worden ſein ſüll / von den vnſern / . Da von wiſſen wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l12">nichts 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch vormals nichts davon gehört </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l13">
<del rend="strikethrough">noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom</expan></del> Dann 
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del> maint Jr / daʒ ew <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l14">ıht genomen 
<del rend="strikethrough">het </del> / . hab / . wenn Jr vns den mitnamen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">benennet </del> / vnd auch was die habe ſeÿ benennet / So </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l16">wollen wir den <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / darvmb <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cʒe rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l17"><expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ew darauf ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>vvıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen / ob die <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r1l18"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> an vns <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_460" id="229v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> und Erasem <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Wisentaw, gebrüdern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Fricz und Erasem, als ir
                                                uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                habt, wie ew und den ewrn nu czü
                                                  <expan>Huntshawbt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>und auf den <expan>güt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ir
                                                  habe</add>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> worden sein süll von
                                                den unsern, da von wissen wir nichts; dann maint ir,
                                                daz ew <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht genomen hab,
                                                wenn ir uns den mit namen und auch, was die habe
                                                sey, benennet, so wollen wir den
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darumb
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cze rede
                                                  <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und ew darauf ein
                                                  <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen, ob die
                                                  <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> an uns
                                                  <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>.</ab>
</div>
